{"tid":1771834,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"希望黃店會響應職工盟 今年加薪5%","createTime":"2019-12-06T06:48:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-06T12:24:47.000Z","uid":84408,"like":16,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"199f3726fc839ddf28352949820e685ab362b3ab","tid":1771834,"uid":84408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T06:48:27.000Z","msg":"老老豆豆 呢半年大家捐民陣捐星火已經好多錢<br />\n黃店小本經營 成日見到一捐就幾萬<br />\n作為小市民見到真係好感概<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但都希望大家關注埋勞工權益呢個問題<br />\n呢個運動 雖然黃藍店都一定會影響到<br />\n但真心希望有賺嘅黃店<br />\n可以幫工友加多少少人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我作為顧客真係寧願先加人工比伙記<br />\n再捐錢比星火民陣<br />\n<br />\n抗爭真係好長期戰 做得黃店嘅伙計<br />\n可能都有份去前線或者捐錢出黎<br />\n香港地生活唔易<br />\n<br />\n希望各位老闆仔可以響應<br />\n打卡上 facebook 支持下今年個方案<br />\n<br />\n對個經濟圈其實好大影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b13dd4b25ef6a8b3492a2bd50029ac784ee31d88","tid":1771834,"uid":84408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T06:50:49.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望大家除咗捐錢比中咗招嘅手足<br />\n<br />\n都要令更多人覺醒 發現原來黃店係有賺<br />\n就算捐埋都係有賺"},{"pid":"ece9e683a79ac6915b6f4b431f3350445d9e3f1f","tid":1771834,"uid":49955,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T06:53:34.000Z","msg":"花紅算啦<br />\n個個月咁好生意咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b8f21e79445fca41b1b3b0324672043b9af59ca","tid":1771834,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T06:53:38.000Z","msg